                            </li>
                            <li class="task-item flex items-start py-2 px-3 hover:bg-slate-50 rounded-md ml-6">
                                <input type="checkbox" data-parent-section="month3" class="form-checkbox task-checkbox h-5 w-5 text-sky-600 rounded border-gray-300 focus:ring-sky-500 mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">
                                <span class="task-text text-slate-700 flex-grow">Как работают HTTPS и TLS? (рукопожатие, сертификаты, шифрование)</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="task-item flex items-start py-2 px-3 hover:bg-slate-50 rounded-md ml-6">
                                <input type="checkbox" data-parent-section="month3" class="form-checkbox task-checkbox h-5 w-5 text-sky-600 rounded border-gray-300 focus:ring-sky-500 mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">
                                <span class="task-text text-slate-700 flex-grow">Как безопасно управлять секретами и переменными окружения? (<code class="code-tag bg-slate-200 text-slate-600 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-xs">.env</code>, Vault, переменные среды в CI/CD)</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="task-item flex items-start py-2 px-3 hover:bg-slate-50 rounded-md ml-6">
                                <input type="checkbox" data-parent-section="month3" class="form-checkbox task-checkbox h-5 w-5 text-sky-600 rounded border-gray-300 focus:ring-sky-500 mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">
                                <span class="task-text text-slate-700 flex-grow">Как найти уязвимость с помощью <strong class="font-semibold">SAST</strong> (на примере <code class="code-tag bg-slate-200 text-slate-600 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-xs">gosec</code> или <code class="code-tag bg-slate-200 text-slate-600 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-xs">Semgrep</code>)?</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="task-item flex items-start py-2 px-3 hover:bg-slate-50 rounded-md ml-6">
                                <input type="checkbox" data-parent-section="month3" class="form-checkbox task-checkbox h-5 w-5 text-sky-600 rounded border-gray-300 focus:ring-sky-500 mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">
                                <span class="task-text text-slate-700 flex-grow">Как работает <strong class="font-semibold">DAST</strong> (на примере <code class="code-tag bg-slate-200 text-slate-600 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-xs">OWASP ZAP</code>)?</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="task-item flex items-start py-2 px-3 hover:bg-slate-50 rounded-md ml-6">
                                <input type="checkbox" data-parent-section="month3" class="form-checkbox task-checkbox h-5 w-5 text-sky-600 rounded border-gray-300 focus:ring-sky-500 mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">
                                <span class="task-text text-slate-700 flex-grow">В чем разница между <code class="code-tag bg-slate-200 text-slate-600 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-xs">Burp Suite</code> и <code class="code-tag bg-slate-200 text-slate-600 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-xs">OWASP ZAP</code>? Когда какой инструмент предпочтительнее?</span>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </section>

                <section id="additional" data-section-id="additional" class="tab-content hidden space-y-6">
                    <div class="p-4 bg-sky-50 rounded-lg border border-sky-200">
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-sky-700 mb-3">Дополнительно: навыки по требованиям вакансии</h2>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">Этот раздел включает дополнительные навыки и области знаний, которые часто требуются в вакансиях по AppSec. Их изучение поможет расширить кругозор и повысить конкурентоспособность на рынке труда.</p>
                        <div class="progress-bar-bg rounded-full h-4 mb-1">
                            <div id="additional-progress-bar" class="progress-bar-fill h-4 rounded-full text-xs font-medium text-white text-center p-0.5 leading-none" style="width: 0%;"></div>
                        </div>
                        <p id="additional-progress-text" class="text-xs text-slate-500 text-right">0/0 выполнено</p>
                    </div>
                    <ul class="space-y-2 pl-4 list-none">
                        <li class="task-item flex items-start py-2 px-3 hover:bg-slate-50 rounded-md">
                            <input type="checkbox" data-parent-section="additional" class="form-checkbox task-checkbox h-5 w-5 text-sky-600 rounded border-gray-300 focus:ring-sky-500 mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">
                            <span class="task-text text-slate-700 flex-grow"><strong class="font-semibold">Участие в BugBounty:</strong> зарегистрироваться на платформах (HackerOne, Bugcrowd), изучить реальные репорты, попробовать найти простые баги.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="task-item flex items-start py-2 px-3 hover:bg-slate-50 rounded-md">
                            <input type="checkbox" data-parent-section="additional" class="form-checkbox task-checkbox h-5 w-5 text-sky-600 rounded border-gray-300 focus:ring-sky-500 mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">
                            <span class="task-text text-slate-700 flex-grow"><strong class="font-semibold">Моделирование угроз:</strong> STRIDE, DFD (Data Flow Diagrams) – базовое понимание и применение на простом приложении.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="task-item flex items-start py-2 px-3 hover:bg-slate-50 rounded-md">
                            <input type="checkbox" data-parent-section="additional" class="form-checkbox task-checkbox h-5 w-5 text-sky-600 rounded border-gray-300 focus:ring-sky-500 mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">
                            <span class="task-text text-slate-700 flex-grow"><strong class="font-semibold">Стандарты (ознакомительно):</strong> OWASP ASVS (Application Security Verification Standard), MITRE CWE Top 25, BSIMM.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="task-item flex items-start py-2 px-3 hover:bg-slate-50 rounded-md">
                            <input type="checkbox" data-parent-section="additional" class="form-checkbox task-checkbox h-5 w-5 text-sky-600 rounded border-gray-300 focus:ring-sky-500 mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">
                            <span class="task-text text-slate-700 flex-grow"><strong class="font-semibold">Контейнеризация:</strong> Углубленная работа с <code class="code-tag bg-slate-200 text-slate-600 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-xs">Docker</code> (не только <code class="code-tag bg-slate-200 text-slate-600 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-xs">DVWA</code>, но и сборка своих Go-приложений). Возможно, основы <code class="code-tag bg-slate-200 text-slate-600 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-xs">Kubernetes (K8s)</code>, если останется время (развертывание приложения, основы безопасности K8s).</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section id="tools" class="tab-content hidden space-y-6">
                     <div class="p-4 bg-sky-50 rounded-lg border border-sky-200">
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-sky-700 mb-3">Инструменты и Платформы</h2>
                        <p class="text-slate-600">Здесь перечислены все инструменты, технологии и платформы, упоминаемые в учебном плане. Этот список поможет вам быстро сориентироваться и найти нужный инструмент в контексте плана.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
                        <div class="p-3 bg-slate-100 rounded-lg shadow"><code class="code-tag text-base text-sky-700 font-semibold">Slurm</code></div>
                        <div class="p-3 bg-slate-100 rounded-lg shadow"><code class="code-tag text-base text-sky-700 font-semibold">openssl</code></div>
                        <div class="p-3 bg-slate-100 rounded-lg shadow"><code class="code-tag text-base text-sky-700 font-semibold">curl</code></div>
                        <div class="p-3 bg-slate-100 rounded-lg shadow"><code class="code-tag text-base text-sky-700 font-semibold">openssl s_client</code></div>
                        <div class="p-3 bg-slate-100 rounded-lg shadow"><code class="code-tag text-base text-sky-700 font-semibold">dig</code></div>
                        <div class="p-3 bg-slate-100 rounded-lg shadow"><code class="code-tag text-base text-sky-700 font-semibold">ping</code></div>
                        <div class="p-3 bg-slate-100 rounded-lg shadow"><code class="code-tag text-base text-sky-700 font-semibold">traceroute</code></div>
                        <div class="p-3 bg-slate-100 rounded-lg shadow"><code class="code-tag text-base text-sky-700 font-semibold">nmap</code></div>
                        <div class="p-3 bg-slate-100 rounded-lg shadow"><code class="code-tag text-base text-sky-700 font-semibold">Burp Suite</code></div>
                        <div class="p-3 bg-slate-100 rounded-lg shadow"><code class="code-tag text-base text-sky-700 font-semibold">OWASP ZAP</code></div>
                        <div class="p-3 bg-slate-100 rounded-lg shadow"><code class="code-tag text-base text-sky-700 font-semibold">mitmproxy</code></div>
                        <div class="p-3 bg-slate-100 rounded-lg shadow"><code class="code-tag text-base text-sky-700 font-semibold">Wireshark</code></div>
                        <div class="p-3 bg-slate-100 rounded-lg shadow"><code class="code-tag text-base text-sky-700 font-semibold">sqlmap</code></div>
                        <div class="p-3 bg-slate-100 rounded-lg shadow"><code class="code-tag text-base text-sky-700 font-semibold">html/template (Go)</code></div>
                        <div class="p-3 bg-slate-100 rounded-lg shadow"><code class="code-tag text-base text-sky-700 font-semibold">text/template (Go)</code></div>
                        <div class="p-3 bg-slate-100 rounded-lg shadow"><code class="code-tag text-base text-sky-700 font-semibold">bcrypt (Go)</code></div>
                        <div class="p-3 bg-slate-100 rounded-lg shadow"><code class="code-tag text-base text-sky-700 font-semibold">Git</code></div>
                        <div class="p-3 bg-slate-100 rounded-lg shadow"><code class="code-tag text-base text-sky-700 font-semibold">gosec</code></div>
                        <div class="p-3 bg-slate-100 rounded-lg shadow"><code class="code-tag text-base text-sky-700 font-semibold">Semgrep</code></div>
                        <div class="p-3 bg-slate-100 rounded-lg shadow"><code class="code-tag text-base text-sky-700 font-semibold">SonarQube</code></div>
                        <div class="p-3 bg-slate-100 rounded-lg shadow"><code class="code-tag text-base text-sky-700 font-semibold">Nuclei</code></div>
                        <div class="p-3 bg-slate-100 rounded-lg shadow"><code class="code-tag text-base text-sky-700 font-semibold">GitLab CI/CD</code></div>
                        <div class="p-3 bg-slate-100 rounded-lg shadow"><code class="code-tag text-base text-sky-700 font-semibold">Docker</code></div>
                        <div class="p-3 bg-slate-100 rounded-lg shadow"><code class="code-tag text-base text-sky-700 font-semibold">Kubernetes (K8s)</code></div>
                        <div class="p-3 bg-slate-100 rounded-lg shadow"><code class="code-tag text-base text-sky-700 font-semibold">PortSwigger Academy</code></div>
                        <div class="p-3 bg-slate-100 rounded-lg shadow"><code class="code-tag text-base text-sky-700 font-semibold">DVWA</code></div>
                    </div>
                </section>
            </main>
        </div>
        <footer class="text-center text-sm text-slate-500 mt-12 pb-8">
            Интерактивный учебный план &copy; 2025
        </footer>
    </div>

    <script type="module">
        import { initializeApp } from "https://www.gstatic.com/firebasejs/11.6.1/firebase-app.js";
        import { getAuth, signInAnonymously, signInWithCustomToken, onAuthStateChanged } from "https://www.gstatic.com/firebasejs/11.6.1/firebase-auth.js";
        import { getFirestore, doc, getDoc, setDoc, collection, getDocs, setLogLevel } from "https://www.gstatic.com/firebasejs/11.6.1/firebase-firestore.js";

        const firebaseConfig = typeof __firebase_config !== 'undefined' ? JSON.parse(__firebase_config) : null;
        const appId = typeof __app_id !== 'undefined' ? __app_id : 'default-study-plan';
        
        let db, auth, userId;
        let appInitialized = false;
        const loadingOverlay = document.getElementById('loading-overlay');

        const sectionIds = ['month1', 'month2', 'month3', 'additional'];

        function showLoading(show) {
            if (loadingOverlay) {
                loadingOverlay.style.display = show ? 'flex' : 'none';
            }
        }

        function updateSectionProgress(sectionId) {
            const sectionElement = document.getElementById(sectionId);
            if (!sectionElement) return;

            const checkboxesInSection = sectionElement.querySelectorAll('.task-checkbox');
            const totalTasks = checkboxesInSection.length;
            let completedTasks = 0;
            checkboxesInSection.forEach(cb => {
                if (cb.checked) {
                    completedTasks++;
                }
            });

            const progressPercentage = totalTasks > 0 ? (completedTasks / totalTasks) * 100 : 0;
            
            const progressBar = document.getElementById(`${sectionId}-progress-bar`);
            const progressText = document.getElementById(`${sectionId}-progress-text`);

            if (progressBar) {
                progressBar.style.width = `${progressPercentage}%`;
                progressBar.textContent = totalTasks > 0 && progressPercentage > 10 ? `${Math.round(progressPercentage)}%` : '';
            }
            if (progressText) {
                progressText.textContent = `${completedTasks}/${totalTasks} выполнено`;
            }
        }

        function updateTotalProgress() {
            let grandTotalTasks = 0;
            let grandCompletedTasks = 0;

            sectionIds.forEach(id => {
                const sectionElement = document.getElementById(id);
                if (sectionElement) {
                    const checkboxesInSection = sectionElement.querySelectorAll('.task-checkbox');
                    grandTotalTasks += checkboxesInSection.length;
                    checkboxesInSection.forEach(cb => {
                        if (cb.checked) {
                            grandCompletedTasks++;
                        }
                    });
                }
            });
            
            const totalProgressPercentage = grandTotalTasks > 0 ? (grandCompletedTasks / grandTotalTasks) * 100 : 0;
            const totalProgressBar = document.getElementById('total-progress-bar');
            const totalProgressText = document.getElementById('total-progress-text');

            if (totalProgressBar) {
                totalProgressBar.style.width = `${totalProgressPercentage}%`;
                totalProgressBar.textContent = grandTotalTasks > 0 && totalProgressPercentage > 5 ? `${Math.round(totalProgressPercentage)}%` : '';
            }
            if (totalProgressText) {
                totalProgressText.textContent = `${grandCompletedTasks}/${grandTotalTasks} выполнено`;
            }
        }
        
        function updateAllProgressDisplays() {
            sectionIds.forEach(id => updateSectionProgress(id));
            updateTotalProgress();
        }

        function assignTaskIds() {
            const sections = document.querySelectorAll('.tab-content[data-section-id]');
            sections.forEach(section => {
                const sectionId = section.dataset.sectionId;
                const checkboxes = section.querySelectorAll('.task-checkbox');
                checkboxes.forEach((checkbox, index) => {
                    checkbox.dataset.taskId = `${sectionId}_${index}`;
                });
            });
        }

        async function loadTaskStatesFromFirestore() {
            if (!userId || !db) {
                console.warn("Firestore not ready or user not logged in for loading tasks.");
                updateAllProgressDisplays(); 
                showLoading(false);
                return;
            }
            showLoading(true);
            try {
                const tasksCollectionPath = `artifacts/${appId}/users/${userId}/securityStudyPlanTasks`;
                const querySnapshot = await getDocs(collection(db, tasksCollectionPath));
                
                querySnapshot.forEach((docSnap) => {
                    const taskId = docSnap.id;
                    const taskData = docSnap.data();
                    const checkbox = document.querySelector(`.task-checkbox[data-task-id="${taskId}"]`);
                    if (checkbox) {
                        checkbox.checked = taskData.completed === true;
                        const taskTextSpan = checkbox.nextElementSibling;
                        if (taskTextSpan && taskTextSpan.classList.contains('task-text')) {
                             if (checkbox.checked) {
                                taskTextSpan.classList.add('text-slate-500', 'line-through');
                            } else {
                                taskTextSpan.classList.remove('text-slate-500', 'line-through');
                            }
                        }
                    }
                });
            } catch (error) {
                console.error("Error loading tasks from Firestore:", error);
            } finally {
                updateAllProgressDisplays();
                showLoading(false);
            }
        }

        async function saveTaskStateToFirestore(taskId, isCompleted) {
            if (!userId || !db) {
                console.warn("Firestore not ready or user not logged in for saving task.");
                return;
            }
            try {
                const taskDocPath = `artifacts/${appId}/users/${userId}/securityStudyPlanTasks/${taskId}`;
                await setDoc(doc(db, taskDocPath), { completed: isCompleted }, { merge: true });
            } catch (error) {
                console.error("Error saving task to Firestore:", error);
            }
        }

        function setupTabNavigation() {
            const tabs = document.querySelectorAll('.tab-button');
            const contents = document.querySelectorAll('.tab-content');
            tabs.forEach(tab => {
                tab.addEventListener('click', () => {
                    tabs.forEach(t => t.classList.remove('active'));
                    tab.classList.add('active');
                    
                    const targetTab = tab.getAttribute('data-tab');
                    contents.forEach(content => {
                        content.classList.toggle('hidden', content.id !== targetTab);
                    });
                });
            });
        }

        function setupCheckboxListeners() {
            const taskCheckboxes = document.querySelectorAll('.task-checkbox');
            taskCheckboxes.forEach(checkbox => {
                checkbox.addEventListener('change', (event) => {
                    const targetCheckbox = event.target;
                    const parentSectionId = targetCheckbox.getAttribute('data-parent-section');
                    const taskId = targetCheckbox.dataset.taskId;

                    if (taskId) {
                        saveTaskStateToFirestore(taskId, targetCheckbox.checked);
                    }
                    
                    const taskTextSpan = targetCheckbox.nextElementSibling;
                    if (taskTextSpan && taskTextSpan.classList.contains('task-text')) {
                        if (targetCheckbox.checked) {
                            taskTextSpan.classList.add('text-slate-500', 'line-through');
                        } else {
                            taskTextSpan.classList.remove('text-slate-500', 'line-through');
                        }
                    }

                    if (parentSectionId) {
                         updateSectionProgress(parentSectionId);
                    }
                    updateTotalProgress();
                });
            });
        }
        
        async function initializeAppLogic() {
            if (!firebaseConfig) {
                console.error("Firebase configuration is missing!");
                showLoading(false);
                assignTaskIds(); 
                setupTabNavigation();
                setupCheckboxListeners();
                updateAllProgressDisplays();
                document.getElementById('user-id-display').textContent = `(Ошибка конфигурации)`;
                return;
            }

            try {
                const firebaseApp = initializeApp(firebaseConfig);
                auth = getAuth(firebaseApp);
                db = getFirestore(firebaseApp);
                // setLogLevel('debug'); 
                appInitialized = true;

                assignTaskIds(); 
                setupTabNavigation();

                onAuthStateChanged(auth, async (user) => {
                    const userIdDisplay = document.getElementById('user-id-display');
                    if (user) {
                        userId = user.uid;
                        userIdDisplay.textContent = `(UID: ${userId.substring(0,8)}...)`;
                        await loadTaskStatesFromFirestore(); 
                    } else {
                        userId = null; 
                        userIdDisplay.textContent = `(Анонимный пользователь)`;
                        updateAllProgressDisplays(); 
                        showLoading(false);
                    }
                    setupCheckboxListeners(); 
                });

                if (typeof __initial_auth_token !== 'undefined' && __initial_auth_token) {
                    try {
                        await signInWithCustomToken(auth, __initial_auth_token);
                    } catch (error) {
                        console.error("Error signing in with custom token, trying anonymous:", error);
                        await signInAnonymously(auth);
                    }
                } else {
                    await signInAnonymously(auth);
                }

            } catch (error) {
                console.error("Firebase initialization failed:", error);
                showLoading(false);
                assignTaskIds();
                setupTabNavigation();
                setupCheckboxListeners();
                updateAllProgressDisplays();
                document.getElementById('user-id-display').textContent = `(Ошибка инициализации)`;
            }
        }

        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', initializeAppLogic);
    </script>
</body>
</html>
